description: AMUNDI ETF LEVERAGED MSCI USA DAILY UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI USA Leveraged 2x Daily strategy Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This index, in Euros, measures the performance based on a double exposure (positive or negative) to the MSCI USA Index, through a short-term loan. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi ETF Leveraged MSCI USA Daily UCITS ETF - EUR
